  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK656">
<l>īṉṟāḷ pacikāṇpā ṉāyiṉuñ ceyyaṟka </l>
<l>cāṉṟōr paḻikkum viṉai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though a minister may see his mother starve let him do not act which the wise would (treat with contempt).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
